        <mxCell id="gKPXw5VkSOpaEjGgAY0d-1" value="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot; color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;＊一檔&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;etf_id&lt;/span&gt;會有三筆紀錄：從&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; isolation: auto;&quot; class=&quot;notion-enable-hover&quot; data-token-index=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(213, 232, 212);&quot;&gt;etf_backtests&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;end_date&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;回推前一年、前三年、前十年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;若該檔&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 242, 204);&quot;&gt;etf_id&lt;/span&gt;的年資沒有一年、三年或十年那麼久，則那個年限不被記錄；且&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: -webkit-standard; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;如果資料不足，該期間的回測就標記「無效」，而&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;不被記錄&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="sketch=0;points=[[0,0,0],[0.25,0,0],[0.5,0,0],[0.75,0,0],[1,0,0],[1,0.25,0],[1,0.5,0],[1,0.75,0],[1,1,0],[0.75,1,0],[0.5,1,0],[0.25,1,0],[0,1,0],[0,0.75,0],[0,0.5,0],[0,0.25,0]];rounded=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=2;html=1;strokeColor=none;gradientColor=none;shadow=0;dashed=0;fontSize=12;fontColor=#9E9E9E;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;spacingTop=-4;whiteSpace=wrap;" parent="1" vertex="1">
